transcript.sentence: 10 times stupid people got punished in the best way.
Video one, two cars street race through an intersection, turning left side by side.
The car in the left lane with the dash cam is overtaken and passed on the right by the red classic muscle car.
It starts to joel and then bounce up and down. And then the rear axle completely disconnects from the car, and it comes to a stop with two wheels up front and no wheels in the back.
Video to
on a 4 lane freeway. The leftmost lane is an express only lane.
A white city n merges out of the express lane and a traffic in a no merge sown.
It is immediately spotted by a police car.
The police car pulls over the sedan,
busted!
Video three,
a red corvette revs its engine and then burns out.
The driver loses control and fears off road into some trees.
Video for
a surveillance camera spots a man in a hoodie approach a parked white sedan.
There is sport commentary playing, ironically as though explaining the actions of the man.
The man throws a brick at the passenger side window. The brick bounces off the window and hits the man in the face.
He collapses just like he was knocked out by a big right hook.
This clip is then replayed in slow motion.
Video five on a 3 lane highway. After the rain, a cart speeds down the middle lane.
Her car loses control and swerved in and out of the left lane until finally it hits and knocks over a light posts.
Video six,
a man who parked illegally in a handicap spot comes back to find his car covered in hundreds of blue posted notes with white posted notes in the shape of a handicap symbol,
much like a handicap parking sign.
He angrily tries to clear them off so that he can drive away. While a large crowd laughs at him while filming on cell phones.
The man rolls down his window and gets into the car and drives off angrily.
Video seven, a blue convertible turns into the left lane from an intersection at a high speed.
The car loses control, spins 180 degrees, and hits the curb.
When it hits the curb, the back wheels are damaged in the trunk, pops open.
Video eight
on a residential one way street. A car passes a bike very closely there. Then both stopped in an intersection.
The driver then chases the biker down the sidewalk. He tries to kick the bike and then stumbles and falls down, rolling completely over on one shoulder.
The clip of the man falling is replayed in slow motion with an animated cape superimposed on the man's back.
Video nine,
a red fast back muscle car burns out. It then loses control and hit the street lamp.
Video 10,
a motorcyclist stopped at an intersection.
The driver of the car behind him, a bald man in shorts and flip flops, approaches the biker.
The man punches the biker in the helmet and is then pushed away.
The girl riding on the back of the motorcycle then hops off and the man shoves her back.
The biker has gotten off his bike. The man continues to try and punch him.
Her breaker pushes the man to the ground and hold them down by his neck.
The man's face looks very funny with wide eyes and bad teeth. The face of golomb from lord of the rings is comically superimposed on his face due to the resemblance.
Bonus clip.
A small hatchback is in the left lane of a 1 way tunnel. A shot of the internet video of keyboard cat is intersected with a cat raising its paws above the keyboard.
In the tunnel, a motorcycle pulls up to the right of the hatchback.
Another shot is intersected of keyboard. Cat with its paws still held above the keyboard, closing its eyes in anticipation.
The motorcyclist kicks the hatchback and then loses his balance. He falls over with his bike, hitting and bouncing off the median.
The screen then goes back to keyboard cat
playing the keyboard.
